                "invention-title": [
                    "Anaerobic fermentation and hydrothermal carbonization multi-source organic solid waste low-carbon combustion system and method",
                    "厌氧发酵及水热碳化的多源有机固废低碳燃烧系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a multi-source organic solid waste low-carbon combustion system and method for anaerobic fermentation and hydrothermal carbonization, and belongs to the technical field of organic solid waste energy regeneration. An oil filtering device is communicated with a drying device, the drying device is communicated with a garbage crushing device, the garbage crushing device is communicated with an anaerobic generation system, a sludge drying device is communicated with the anaerobic generation system, and the sludge drying device is communicated with the sludge generation system; the anaerobic generation system is communicated with the water vapor reforming hydrogen production unit, the water vapor generator is communicated with the water vapor reforming hydrogen production unit, one side of the water vapor reforming hydrogen production unit is communicated with the Harberg method ammonia gas preparation device, the other side of the water vapor reforming hydrogen production unit is communicated with the ammonia-hydrogen engine system, and the Harberg method ammonia gas preparation device is communicated with the ammonia-hydrogen engine system. And the low-temperature air fractionation device is communicated with the Harber-process ammonia gas preparation device. The device has the advantages that the hydrogen yield of kitchen garbage and sludge serving as raw materials is effectively increased through the methane steam reforming hydrogen production unit, energy utilization of the sludge is achieved by preparing hydrothermal carbon, and low-carbon combustion is achieved while mechanical energy is generated."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了厌氧发酵及水热碳化的多源有机固废低碳燃烧系统及方法，属于有机固废能源再生技术领域，滤油装置与干燥装置连通，干燥装置与垃圾粉碎装置连通，垃圾粉碎装置与厌氧发生系统连通，污泥干燥装置与厌氧发生系统连通，厌氧发生系统与水蒸气重整制氢单元连通，水蒸气发生器与水蒸气重整制氢单元连通，水蒸气重整制氢单元一侧与哈伯法制氨气装置连通，另一侧与氨氢发动机系统连通，哈伯法制氨气装置与氨氢发动机系统连通，低温空气分馏装置与哈伯法制氨气装置连通。本发明具有通过甲烷的水蒸气重整制氢单元，有效提升以厨余垃圾和污泥为原料的氢气产率，通过制备水热炭，实现污泥的能源化利用，在产生机械能的同时，实现低碳燃烧的优点。"
                }
